{"tid":2331304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：2020年基本法無對公務員國籍或護照訂明要求","createTime":"2020-12-18T16:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T18:22:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45834edc4ce7f7729835ec3d402d5c0a14911d16","tid":2331304,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局稱基本法無對公務員國籍或護照訂明要求<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局表示，《基本法》並無對公務員的國籍或所持有的護照訂明要求。<br />\n<br />\n常任秘書長、部門首長和屬首長級薪級表第6點或以上的公務員今日宣誓，擁護《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區基本法》，以及效忠中華人民共和國香港特別行政區。本台向公務員事務局查詢有關常任秘書長、部門首長及高級首長級公務員，持有外國國籍或英國國民(海外)護照的情況。<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局回覆查詢時未有交代有關數字，局方回應指根據《基本法》第99條，除了在《基本法》第101條指明的例外情況，在香港特區政府各部門任職的公務人員，必須是香港特別行政區永久性居民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566114-20201218.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566114-20201218.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=85b74b35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566114-20201218.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=182bb800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566114-20201218.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"be7c0096db81f0624747f17166cd5614ff373da5","tid":2331304,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:18:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffdac4254cff3a3fcf210c6106c21b174e2e7dc6","tid":2331304,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"基本法冇講啫，宣誓對象 兒元首 隨時可以下旨"},{"pid":"4ca8233b7120015625c199a3de9ea6ae4a1841cf","tid":2331304,"uid":276273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"支那法律無寫唔等於可以，<br />\n寫咗唔等於唔可以歪曲。<br />\n<br />\n最On9，A 國民效忠 B 國家法律，e個仲係咪A 國民呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240b96dbbf5edaf7057d3eae62c3df6e0587c723","tid":2331304,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16245a002b90728a0d8c8a0d433aef2f4fb9a4d","tid":2331304,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"冇話得咪即係唔可以囉！！啲思考都唔同大陸接軌既？？"},{"pid":"ca52a5a55bc7d428655201e9d2ff31f05e4a1a21","tid":2331304,"uid":120253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"基本法都無要求公務員宣誓啦, 咁你又做"},{"pid":"b960190015528696113af79b0fd5a5edab6a135f","tid":2331304,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T18:22:34.000Z","msg":"基本法無寫咪擺落附件三囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}